1889181880.text: "Analysis of SOCS expression in a variety of cell types by Tannahill et al. [XREF_BIBR] revealed a reciprocal regulation of SOCS2 expression on SOCS3 levels, resulting in impaired SOCS3 mediated suppression of STAT3 and STAT5b activation and cell proliferation by IL-3 when SOCS2 levels are enhanced [XREF_BIBR]."
